profile:
Dean Clayworth, a licensed tradesman, established Lambeth Home Maintenance as one of the premier renovation and maintenance companies in London. His meticulous workmanship and eye for detail and design have earned him a reputation for doing exceptional quality work with a respected work ethic.

About the Company:

Lambeth Home Maintenance (LHM) is proud to have been renovating, repairing, and servicing homes and small offices in London and the surrounding area since 2008.

Through hard work and genuine respect for others, Lambeth Home Maintenance now enjoys being known for maintaining the highest levels of professionalism, knowledge and integrity with clients, suppliers and other contractors alike.

We are reliable and punctual so we don’t waste your time.
We use the best tools and materials available so that we can give you the highest quality finished product.
We require that our employees be trained on safety practices to prevent accidents. We are insured and have WSIB coverage to keep you free from liability.
We are members of the Better Business Bureau with an “A+” rating, and we are the number one ranked handyman services provider in London on Homestars so you know we are credible with no complaints against us.
We insist on the highest quality of work from our employees and any sub-trades we bring in to the job so that you get the best workmanship possible.
We clean up after ourselves so that your home has as few disruptions as possible during the project.
And most importantly, we do everything we possibly can to make sure you are happy with the job we have done for you!
